================================================================================
OIL REWARDS — SUPABASE REFACTOR SPECIFICATION & IMPLEMENTATION GUIDE
================================================================================

1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Convert Oil Rewards from a json-server backend to Supabase (Postgres + Auth).
The flat "services" table is replaced by two relational tables:
  - logged_services   (oil change visits)
  - loyalty_redemptions (free-service redemptions)

A Supabase Auth login page gates all application access. All existing UI
workflows remain identical. The architecture is designed so that once a
Supabase project is provisioned, only two values (URL + anon key) need to be
supplied in a single config file.


